name: 144MHz Quarter Wave Antenna
description:
144MHz Quarter Wave Whip Antenna
• Tuned for the 2m (144MHz) Amateur Radio Band
• Available in Black, Red, Green or Blue colors
• SMA Female Connector (fits Baofeng & other Chinese radios)
• Quarter Wavelength on VHF 144MHz, Three-Quarter Wavelength on UHF 440MHz

name: 224MHz Quarter Wave Antenna
description:
223MHz Quarter Wave Whip Antenna
• Tuned for the 1.25m (223MHz) Amateur Radio Band
• Available in Black, Red, Green or Blue colors
• SMA Female Connector (fits Baofeng & other Chinese radios)
